This paper focuses on improving the quality of user-generated text content in social media through automatic feedback. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) as these fields deal with natural language processing, text analysis, and automated feedback systems. Additionally, the paper discusses user studies and the design of a feedback interface, which suggests that it may also belong to the categories of Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
